## Bug 3 — Finesse Shot PlayStyle Weak Output
**Platform:** PS5/PC
**Severity:** High
**Status:** Under Investigation — EA Trello
**Jira ID:** MP-3

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Select player with Finesse Shot PlayStyle
2. Get into shooting position
3. Press R1 + Circle

**Expected:** Fast accurate finesse shot
